source_refs.context:
The motivation for performing a clustering analysis has been given in Sect.\,\ref{kin}. We did so on the stars of our sample using the HDBSCAN\footnote{\url{https://hdbscan.readthedocs.io/en/latest/index.html}} 
library and a Gaussian Mixture model\footnote{\url{https://scikit-learn.org/stable/modules/mixture. html}}.
After a number of attempts using different input variables, we decided to use E, L$_Z$ and J$_R$ only. The data was scaled using a `RobustScaler' within the scikit learn package.

